---
title: Pork Pizza Burger with Pizza Sauce and Mozzarella Cheese
description: This pork pizza burger with Italian herbs is the new dish in town. Italian and garlic spiced pork is topped with pizza sauce and mozzarella cheese and then sandwiched between toasted garlic and parm buns! Crispy sweet potato wedges are the perfect pairing for this heavy-hitter.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burger-au-porc-style-pizza-08ec9c04.jpg
